      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HARA HACHI BU (1) goes very well at the course and distance with three wins and a placing from seven starts. In the money last time at this track (23.19) in a Free For All, finishing a 4.5 lengths second. Looks suited and should go close. MEPUNGA SCARLETT (4) is in hot form winning her last three on end, the latest pinging the lids with a sensational early split and clocking 25.13 over 450m at Shepparton. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Form should stack up. PAW OLYMPUS (8) was strongly supported last start when a short priced favourite and duly saluted winning by 4.5 lengths at this track in a handy 22.91. Wide box to overcome but likes the trip. Has a strong record from box 8, including two wins. Has definite claims. PAW WINKWORTH (6) is always hard to beat when drawn in this box.",
